info.name: Naked Veggie Taco
info.description: Introducing the Naked Veggie Taco – a fresh twist on a classic! With a vibrant taco shell made entirely of vegetables, it’s a burst of flavor and crunch in every bite. Filled with spicy harissa sauce, tangy hot red salsa, zesty pico de gallo, and crisp iceberg lettuce, this taco is perfect for those who want to indulge in something wholesome yet bold. Enjoy a taco experience like never before, where the shell is as good as the filling!
